<P>
CELEBRATION: THOUSANDS OF IRISH AND NON-IRISH ALIKE MARK THE SAINT'S DAY WITH 
STEP DANCERS, BAGPIPERS, A PARADE AND PLENTY OF IRISH BEER. 
